00:40:44.383 --> 00:40:45.702
E' chiaro, Doug.

712
00:40:45.802 --> 00:40:48.449
Quando mi dovro' ritirare,
quando verra' quel giorno,


713
00:40:48.549 --> 00:40:50.692
